respiratory tract infection.

141
00:06:42,919 --> 00:06:44,902
She's such a good woman.

142
00:06:44,938 --> 00:06:46,921
And her family...

143
00:06:46,974 --> 00:06:48,250
- so wonderful.
- Dr. Cain,

144
00:06:48,274 --> 00:06:51,292
are her children aware that
she's not gonna be waking up?

145
00:06:51,328 --> 00:06:54,112
Absolutely not. Because we
don't know that for sure yet.

146
00:06:54,147 --> 00:06:56,364
The brain is an enigma.
Anything can happen.

147
00:06:56,399 --> 00:06:58,366
Of course, but...

148
00:06:58,401 --> 00:06:59,934
